About

  MarkdownJPlugin is a Blojsom plugin that converts {{{http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/}Markdown}} syntax
  to HTML using {{{http://markdownj.petebevin.com}MarkdownJ}} .

  This plugin will hopefully replace the current plugin implementation that calls Markdown Perl script (issue {{{http://jira.blojsom.com/jira/browse/BLOJSOM-233}BLOJSOM-233}}).

